nl.esciencecenter.octopus

Enum OctopusPropertyDescription.Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OctopusPropertyDescription.Component>
      • nl.esciencecenter.octopus.OctopusPropertyDescription.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<OctopusPropertyDescription.Component>
    Enclosing interface:
    OctopusPropertyDescription

    public static enum OctopusPropertyDescription.Component
extends Enum<OctopusPropertyDescription.Component>
    The Component enumeration lists all possible parts of octopus for which a property can be provided.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CREDENTIALS
      Properties for CREDENTIAL components can be passed to the various newCredential calls in Credentials.
      FILESYSTEM
      Properties for FILESYSTEM components can be passed to Files.newFileSystem(String, String, Credential, Map).
      OCTOPUS
      Properties for OCTOPUS components can be passed to OctopusFactory.newOctopus(Map).
      SCHEDULER
      Properties for SCHEDULER components can be passed to Jobs.newScheduler(String, String, Credential, Map).
